### [1 Chronicles Chapter 19](../../../bib/kjv/ch1019.htm#001.md)

[1 Chronicles](../../../bib/kjv/ch1001.htm#001.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_000">ch1 19:0</span></span>

Overview

[Ch1 19:1](../../../bib/kjv/ch1019.htm#001.md), David's messengers, sent to
comfort Hanun, the son of Nahash, are villainously treated; [Ch1
19:6](../../../bib/kjv/ch1019.htm#006.md), The Ammonites, strengthened by
the Syrians, are overcome by Joab and Abishai; [Ch1
19:16](../../../bib/kjv/ch1019.htm#016.md), Shophach, making a new supply
of the Syrians, is slain by David.

